Output filename           | UNCHANGED    | hardcoded separate | case+date template
File rotation             | automatic    | none (monolithic)  | date-based
Grid in output            | (lon,lat)    | (lon,lat)         | (lon,lat) (OK)
Fields remapped           | ALL on tape  | hardcoded subset  | ALL in stream
3D field handling         | native dims  | split per-level   | 3D with depth dim
